lead_paragraph: Henrik Lundqvist made 27 saves and the New York Rangers posted their first three-game winning streak since November with a 2-1 victory over the New Jersey Devils on Monday night.

headline.print_headline: Lundqvist Makes 27 Saves, Rangers Win Third in Row
